1
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:06,960
Watch out, Heir.

2
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,690
General Pei.

3
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:12,690
General Pei.

4
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,880
Jinlin Guards, hear my order.

5
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:19,600
Kill the rebels of Prince Ling.

6
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:20,720
Leave no one alive.

7
00:01:21,080 --> 00:01:23,010
Whoever brings Prince Ling's head

8
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:24,620
will be heavily rewarded.

9
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,200
You bastards.

10
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:31,480
Die.

11
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,720
My eyes.

12
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:38,240
I can't see.

13
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:41,240
Call the imperial doctor.

14
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:44,640
Prince,

15
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:46,280
take care.

16
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,280
Cui Tingru.

17
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,760
For the past three years,

18
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,800
I have waited for this moment every single day.

19
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,720
You framed my father

20
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,450
and brutally killed my mother.

21
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:23,720
Today,

22
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,800
I will make you pay blood for blood

23
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,920
and a life for a life.

24
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,800
Winners take all.

25
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,800
Kill me if you want,

26
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,840
no need for words.

27
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,600
Tell me the Duke's whereabouts,

28
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,290
and I'll leave your corpse intact.

29
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,800
You will never see him again.

30
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:12,480
Let me out!

31
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,400
I am the son of the Minister of Works.

32
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,240
If you set me free,

33
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:23,200
I will not hesitate to reward you with official titles and nobility.

34
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,640
I am a trusted follower of the Empress Dowager.

35
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:27,840
How dare you imprison me?

36
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:30,640
When I return to see the Empress Dowager,

37
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:34,079
I will have you all cut into a thousand pieces.

38
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,079
Who?

39
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:51,290
Who is outside the door?

40
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:53,920
Get me out of here.

41
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:56,340
I'll agree to any condition you have.

42
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,600
Save me. Please save me.

43
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:07,960
No matter how much gold, silver, or treasure you want,

44
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,020
I can give it to you.

45
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:12,600
Does it hurt?

46
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:14,840
Mingli.

47
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,200
You are Mingli.

48
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:20,050
I knew you would come to save me.

49
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,440
I knew it.

50
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,560
You couldn't bear to leave me alone.

51
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,160
Right?

52
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:30,680
Mingli.

53
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,880
Hurry up and take me away from this godforsaken place.

54
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:36,080
This place is right next to Zichen Hall.

55
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,600
There are guards outside.

56
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:40,080
Only when the guards let their guard down at midnight,

57
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,140
can we give it a try.

58
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,320
Okay, okay.

59
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,000
I will listen to you.

60
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,720
I'll do whatever you say.

61
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,400
Have a seat first, Brother Yuheng.

62
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,130
We need to plan this carefully.

63
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,100
Sit down first.

64
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,200
Sit down.

65
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,480
Brother Yuheng,

66
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,320
you can't see it anymore.

67
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,960
From now on,

68
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,880
Yan Qingshu's face,

69
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,600
I no longer have to use it.

70
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:21,600
Reporting to Your Majesty and the Empress Dowager,

71
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:25,160
the heir of Marquis Zhenbei has executed Prince Ling,

72
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,680
and the rebels have all surrendered.

73
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:31,160
Prince Ling's crime of privately forging weapons and armor

74
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,360
was ultimately caused by my past indulgence.

75
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:36,370
Mother, why do you say that?

76
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,920
If you hadn't secretly deployed the Jinlin Guards to help...

77
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:41,000
I fear my attempt to rid the court of corrupt officials this time

78
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,680
will not be entirely successful.

79
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,140
Once this case is settled,

80
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:49,360
I shall go to the imperial mausoleum to accompany the late Emperor

81
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,680
and listen to the whispering pines.

82
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,000
The imperial mausoleum is desolate.

83
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,930
It is no place to reside long-term.

84
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,200
Besides,

85
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:59,409
I still need your constant guidance, Mother.

86
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,080
I am old

87
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,090
and my eyesight is failing.

88
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:08,220
I can barely distinguish the dragon knob on the imperial seal.

89
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,400
But I remember the Vermilion Bird carved

90
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,930
on the late Emperor's dragon-patterned box.

91
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:21,480
It was so lifelike, as if ready to take flight.

92
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:23,800
Mother.

93
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,960
Father's delirious words during his illness years ago,

94
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:28,690
how can you fully believe them?

95
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,380
Eunuch Liu,

96
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,480
bring the dragon-patterned box and a brazier.

97
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,600
Yes, Your Majesty.

98
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,480
Inside the dragon-patterned box,

99
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:43,240
there is a secret edict.

100
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,320
If necessary,

101
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,720
it can keep

102
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:48,800
you and

103
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:53,280
your mother safe.

104
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:34,880
The late Emperor always complained that I overthink things.

105
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,760
Now that the dust has settled,

106
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:41,280
I can finally sleep peacefully.

107
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:43,320
Only when you are well, Mother,

108
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,560
can I sit securely on the throne.

109
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,560
By the grace of Heaven,

110
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,920
the supreme mandate is passed down.

111
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,720
The late Emperor has ascended to Heaven,

112
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,320
and the divine artifacts have found their rightful owner.

113
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:30,040
The current Emperor, Cunye,

114
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:32,000
is wise and respectful,

115
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,120
with virtues matching Heaven and Earth.

116
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,250
He is fit to inherit the great lineage,

117
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,409
and bring eternal peace to the people.

118
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,799
We respectfully present the jade scepter,

119
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:43,000
and devoutly confer the imperial seal.

120
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,360
May you respectfully accept it,

121
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,560
revere the majesty of Heaven,

122
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:50,560
and forever protect the imperial throne.

123
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,320
Cunye,

124
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:13,260
do you truly have the ability to bear the mandate of Heaven?

125
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:15,560
Since I have received the mandate from Heaven,

126
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,520
I shall bear the weight of the empire,

127
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,980
and the trust of the state.

128
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,880
I sit securely on this throne,

129
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,800
and I will hold it firmly.

130
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:39,440
Long live the Emperor!

131
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:26,960
Father is gone.

132
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:30,280
What's the use of crying?

133
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:34,610
The Emperor did not execute the whole family.

134
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,810
It is already a great blessing for the Cui family.

135
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,960
Today, I make the decision

136
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:59,120
to betroth the Princess of Ling to the Heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei.

137
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:02,640
I hope the Heir will cherish and protect her from now on.

138
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:05,580
so as not to fail Linlang's lifelong trust in me.

139
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,760
Xiao Jingyan.

140
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,600
From now on, you and I

141
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,520
are like this jade,

142
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,640
cutting all ties of affection and duty.

143
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,320
You two may rise.

144
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,840
Thank you, Your Majesty.

145
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:51,440
Quelling the rebellion and pacifying the palace is a great service to the state.

146
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:52,440
I am very pleased.

147
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,520
Summoning you two today

148
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,360
is to reward you for your merits.

149
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,120
No need for formalities.

150
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,160
I need no reward.

151
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:00,600
I implore Your Majesty to retry

152
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:02,760
the case of the 3,000 fallen soldiers of the Zhenbei Army,

153
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:04,040
to comfort their loyal souls

154
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,600
and set the record straight for the world.

155
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,440
This case involves the late Emperor's reputation,

156
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,720
it's not appropriate to discuss it again.

157
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:10,780
Prince Xiao, do not cling to the past.

158
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,200
Moreover,

159
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,520
the offense of breaking out of prison this time

160
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,780
I have not yet pursued.

161
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,240
Merits and faults offset each other.

162
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,200
No need to mention it again.

163
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,000
Your Majesty.

164
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,780
Although Prince Ling is dead,

165
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,290
his accomplice Xie Yuheng is still alive.

166
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:27,080
The secret letters I presented before are all here.

167
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,560
Witnesses and material evidence

168
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,560
are all complete.

169
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,760
I once looked through the registry

170
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:39,560
and know that the eldest legitimate daughter of Duke Yan is twenty years old

171
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:40,690
and not yet married.

172
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:41,880
Your Majesty,

173
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:45,280
I implore Your Majesty to grant a marriage.

174
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:47,320
If you stop entangling yourself in the old case,

175
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,850
I will grant you a marriage.

176
00:12:49,280 --> 00:12:51,560
Which lady has Prince Xiao taken a fancy to?

177
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:54,600
This person is far away in the horizon, yet right before your eyes.

178
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:57,800
I want to marry the eldest legitimate daughter of the Duke's estate,

179
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:58,560
Yan Qingshu.

180
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,200
Please grant permission, Your Majesty.

181
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,200
I do not permit it.

182
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:02,850
I am not willing.

183
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,120
Yan Qingshu,

184
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:09,010
since you have no interest in Prince Xiao,

185
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,800
why not enter the palace as a concubine?

186
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:12,800
I will grant you the power to assist in managing the six palaces,

187
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:13,880
with endless favor.

188
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:15,340
I have sworn a solemn oath.

189
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:16,960
With my father's whereabouts unknown,

190
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:19,000
I will absolutely not discuss marriage.

191
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,460
If Your Majesty forces me,

192
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:23,920
Qingshu.

193
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:26,480
today I can only spill my blood in this golden hall

194
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:27,640
to fulfill filial piety and righteousness.

195
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:28,400
Enough.

196
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,400
I order Prince Xiao to thoroughly investigate

197
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,800
the case of Duke Yan's disappearance,

198
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:35,130
and find out the truth within a time limit.

199
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,720
As the daughter of an important minister,

200
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:41,160
how dare you act so rashly about life and death in the Hall of Supreme Harmony!

201
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,090
What an outrage!

202
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,280
I know my crime.

203
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:49,080
Tonight, I am holding a celebratory banquet

204
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:52,050
to reward the meritorious ministers.

205
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,480
You two must attend.

206
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:56,090
- I obey the decree.
- I obey the decree.

207
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,600
Your Highness.

208
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:15,080
His Majesty is slightly unwell

209
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,600
and unable to attend the banquet in person.

210
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,520
He has specially bestowed upon Your Highness

211
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:21,880
wine paid as tribute from the Western Regions

212
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,720
to show his royal favor.

213
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

214
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,800
Cuimei.

215
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:00,260
Cuimei.

216
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:03,040
Huachao.

217
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:03,480
Kun, Huachao.

218
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:03,880
Kun, Huachao.

219
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:04,280
Wei, Kun, Huachao.

220
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:04,540
Wei.

221
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,080
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

222
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:11,200
Shuang, Bin.

223
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:11,640
Shuang, Bin.

224
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,240
Ning, Zheng, Shuang, Bin.

225
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,000
Ning, Zheng.

226
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,000
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

227
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:21,080
Wei, Chao.

228
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:21,640
Wei, Chao.

229
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:23,720
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

230
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,050
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

231
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:41,800
Xi.

232
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:42,760
Tao, Qiang.

233
00:15:46,560 --> 00:15:48,040
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

234
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,040
Yiyi.

235
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:52,640
Yiyi.

236
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:00,440
Sisi.
